Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着大家再次降生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里等着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在流逝的时光中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一刻紧接一刻地死亡  一刻紧接一刻地转生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从无到有的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:52.55,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:59.75,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:15.40,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:25.87,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:37.95,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:48.54,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:54.70,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:02:00.55,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:04.92,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.26,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:11.27,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:52.55,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:59.75,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在倒错的精神世界中相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:15.40,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我们眼里的世界总是相互颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:25.87,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,这几乎要被认定为是无可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:37.95,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口淌泪的眼眸 在内心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:48.54,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的两人来不及结合便听到离别的倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:54.70,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:02:00.55,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们像渐趋衰老的动物一样相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:04.92,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.26,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,在倒错的精神世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:11.27,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我想细细体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===============OP=================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,390)\fs32\fad(600,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1B1B1B&\be5\blur2}爱的野兽们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 尽是些淡而无味的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那家伙会在这…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前那野兽一般的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不经诞生礼节仪式之人不会有真正的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于自黑暗深渊中重生的他们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正好是恰当的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让女人全部退后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的目标是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得这是性别歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是说这话的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快退后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是血肉之躯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想一下白刃战的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给我的洞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是墓穴特训的成果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空间填补
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配合得如此默契
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心有灵犀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫唱妇随
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将填埋的力量转换成了开辟的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢对我耍花招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 你要对Mix做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 这家伙也是香气扑鼻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 他只对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来保护御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸井
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不要妨碍我和臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋居然叫御子乃做臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然连伤害都可以逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直率地朝向想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音…又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽做些奇怪的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在奏响大地与空气而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你那逆转的不谐和音已经耳熟能详了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能被你妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人是只属于…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于我一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一举逆转了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野兽的猛攻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是一种有趣的音色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说他看上了御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人对一个女人穷追不舍的理由只有这一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 男人追男人也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狼吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据诸井发来的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以判断那家伙现正挟持着御子乃潜伏在市内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就在地面进行搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们兵分两路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到那边去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 我也跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 我只是要杀了你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你死在我的臂弯里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影 你听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经把气味的源头弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是使用方式有误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影你睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边已经完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听得很清楚啊 爱的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}未影 快让我回来 未影 快回话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微让我捉弄一下有何不可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁不会妒忌抢先得到心头好的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道? 知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他绝对不会加害于御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么那么肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 他是御子乃命中注定的对像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃的真命天子不是阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闻到了 果然很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么你总是说出这么过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想杀掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 我和你明明无怨无仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你一直待在Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样 现在你在这里把我杀掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我 在这种地方也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要我住手 那我就住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这根本就没住手嘛 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想让我舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想…想杀掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是反语?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只对你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…这双眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉好令人怀念…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲 和我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前也这么叫过我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲和阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神话说的就是我们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创世之初
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在生命之树下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大的生命之树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌管着该星球所有的生灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也掌管着星球自身的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在两个种族的纷争中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳之翼觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且给生命之树授粉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 生命之树的花朵却没有结出果实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那么渐渐枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长此下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这星球将变成永无生命诞生的荒芜之地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真心相爱的阿波隆和希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护生命之树而天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是希尔菲说道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕要等一万两千年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲 你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一万两千年之后再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…阿波隆的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是…阿波隆?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想说御子乃就是希尔菲吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会想出那么荒谬的事情来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我无意中看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也就能跟怪炎那丧服的婚礼的影像衔接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔也看过那影像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波隆什么的 希尔菲什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是个传说而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当真能够如此断定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我稍微有点高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为如果御子乃和那家伙真的是被命运所系的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定…阿马塔和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡 你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝴蝶?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚了还在出没?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…我不是什么希尔菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是…什么希尔菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吓我 希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纠缠不休的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种能够成功的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏特训的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经能把那家伙的力量稍微抵销一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我所愿 他冲着我这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来把将家伙从御子乃身边引开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赶快联络怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这样不就成英雄了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 是御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎说他马上就过来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔你快退后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在御子乃成功逃脱之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得拖延住那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我去…死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死你 我要杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屡次三番地…杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要…要死了吗 我…要死在这里吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要陷入那黑暗的深渊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那黑暗之中…我又要变得孤身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔·空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗再也不是你为情所困而饱受煎熬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是为了斩断如今的执着 缔结新的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 把自己束缚在黑暗和孤独之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃过去和执着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纠缠不休的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆向飞翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 我的力量会不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无执着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不为一切外物所惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 不要掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我收拾掉他之前你就待在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 快给他最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是身处在以命相搏的立场上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开枪 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅这个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如象征着复活的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不被允许的爱啊 尽管苏醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越一万两千年的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------------------ED------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:58.44,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:06.25,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:16.23,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:25.73,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:33.59,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:41.18,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:45.37,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:48.53,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:53.06,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:56.27,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:00.60,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.82,0:24:07.11,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:58.44,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 点缀着雪白的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:06.25,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}从睡梦中惊醒之后 远望着忧伤的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:16.23,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}这份青涩的感觉 依存在绿叶错综的纹路之间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:25.73,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}侧耳聆听 晨露缓缓落下的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:33.59,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所创造的这个世界并不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:41.18,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因为这里每天都有恋情一段接一段地告终
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:45.37,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初尝恋爱的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:48.53,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}这个你应该不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:53.06,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不见天日也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:56.27,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:00.60,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算你把我忘却也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.82,0:24:07.11,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------------------ED------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.41,0:24:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我兴奋并如此发酵的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一万两千年的命运的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.03,0:24:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也委身于这臭气吧 希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要反抗的话 可是会很疼的
